people of the world,

00:04:44.130 --> 00:04:48.180 align:middle line:84%
the Native Americans, the
Indians in South America,

00:04:48.180 --> 00:04:49.920 align:middle line:90%
the druids in Europe.

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:51.900 align:middle line:84%
